ğŸš€ Available Endpoints

ğŸ¯ 1. Initialize Lobby

POST /initialize-lobby

Body:

{
  "match_id": "match_001",
  "life_value": 10000000
}

ğŸ¯ 2. Deposit to Lobby

POST /deposit-to-lobby

Body:

{
  "lobby_address": "3HJb...1fd",
  "player_wallet": "4NkL...m5d",
  "lives_purchased": 10,
  "team": 1
}

ğŸ¯ 3. Start Match

POST /start-match

Body:

{
  "lobby_address": "3HJb...1fd"
}

ğŸ¯ 4. Buy Lives

POST /buy-lives

Body:

{
  "match_address": "8KLp...d1T",
  "player_wallet": "4NkL...m5d",
  "additional_lives": 5
}

ğŸ¯ 5. Submit Match Results

POST /submit-match-results

Body:

{
  "match_address": "8KLp...d1T",
  "final_lives": [
    { "player_wallet": "4NkL...m5d", "lives_held": 15 },
    { "player_wallet": "7JkL...m2c", "lives_held": 5 }
  ],
  "is_valid_match": true
}

ğŸ¯ 6. Cancel Match

POST /cancel-match

Body:

